FMCG : Select Launches 2011-12 # Wendell Rodricks Now At Wills Lifestyle Wendell Rodricks joins leading Indian designers - Rohit Bal, Rajesh Pratap Singh, JJ Valaya, Satya Paul, Ranna Gill, Rohit Gandhi and Rahul Khanna to present a bouquet of their offerings in collaboration with Wills Lifestyle. # Wills Classic Wonderpress Shirts Shirts with advanced liquid ammonia treatment and moist cure to give a sharp and wrinkle free look. <::A man in a light-colored shirt and dark tie, looking to the right, with his hand in his pocket. : figure::> <::A woman sitting on the ground, wearing a patterned top and light-colored skirt, with foliage in the background. : figure::> # John Players Jeans John Players Jeans gives one the perfect vintage look with its comprehensive collection of urban styled denims in textured yarns, in slim and regular fits, with a variety of distressed finishes. <::Three men posing outdoors, with the text "johhplayers je ans" overlaid on the bottom right. : figure::>
